  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But to me, the thought that I can be a few-- whatever days I can be with my dad, try to help him when he was so ill, so that's what gave me this idea to do it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when daddy came down, and he said-- before we part, he looked at me, and he said, remember there is a God and be a Jew.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was his last words when we part.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, I went to Mak-- to Peterswaldau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, the other, a few weeks later, there was another transport came, the other 60.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some other people came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were working for the-- for the-- in a big factory for ammunition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was sent-- I was-- I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, that was just-- coincidentally, they did not assign me to heavy physical work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in a-- we still, we wear our own clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't cut the hair then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was in a very-- comparing with the other departments, I was-- they-- I just worked on those little-- like little, for the bombs, what you like, for the watches, for the time?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What they call this, gears?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Gears within the watch?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little tiny-- yeah, with the tiny little, with the like-- and I had with the-- I had the magnifying glass in my eye.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to control it, to check every little one, which was very strenuous for my vision.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was ammunition, but there were a lot of separate, different kinds of parts to make for the bombs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had [INAUDIBLE] I had this precise work, which was very tiny, which was not very difficult, but you have to strain your eyes, naturally.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And which I lost-- my vision got so weak.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
